why do we need to integrate API.

Integrating the API allows seamless data exchange and automation between your application and NewsBreak's Ad Manager. This integration helps you manage campaigns more efficiently, access real-time data, and automate processes to optimize your advertising efforts. If you're interested in learning more about how to integrate the API, you can check out our detailed guide here: [API Integration Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/27680147056397-API-Integration-Guide).
what if we don't integrate? how will the data exchange be?

If you choose not to integrate the API, data exchange will be limited to manual processes. You'll need to access and manage your campaigns directly through NewsBreak's Ad Manager interface. This means you'll manually track performance, make adjustments, and handle reporting without the automation benefits that API integration provides. While this approach can work, it may require more time and effort compared to automated solutions.
